    public static class TradingOptimizer.TradePair

implements java.lang.Comparable<TradingOptimizer.TradePair>
    TradePair class represents a potential pairing between an importer and exporter Very little is saved in each object, save the relatively expensive efficiency calculation and the Territory references. They may be instantiated from an existing TradePair to mitigate computational complexity.
